{"tid":245440,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[IOS/AN]龍珠Z 爆裂對戰（33）望穿秋水 萬眾期待大亂鬥","createTime":"2017-05-16T08:56:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T09:05:08.000Z","uid":8300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c046040eeab501557701b265cd26ee91049e64c9","tid":245440,"uid":8300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T08:56:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">活動</span></strong><br />\n全世界1億5000万DL!! 大感謝キャンペーン第2弾!!<br />\n05/8 (Mon) ~ 05/22 (Mon)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K4523gw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK4523gw.png&h=00bd0975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://jpn.dbz.space/news/000945\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjpn.dbz.space%2Fnews%2F000945&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=fda9a14c\" target=\"_blank\">https://jpn.dbz.space/news/000945</a><br />\n<br />\n卡池<br />\n秘められた凶悪パワーを持つ新SSRブロリーが登場!! 溢れ出す強大な破壊力に大注目!!<br />\n05/08 (Mon) HKT16:00 ~ 05/25 (Thu) HKT15:59<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28S4Tkc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28S4Tkc.png&h=dc1a2cec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新SSRキャラクターは超強力!! 超系からは超ゴジータ!! 極系からはスーパージャネンバが登場!!<br />\nStart Time: 04/28 HKT 14:15 pm (Fri)<br />\nEnd Time: 05/22 HKT 15:59 pm (Mon)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G8123MJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG8123MJ.png&h=bae3544d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>新手教學</strong></span><br />\n感謝 冥幣巴整合 <br />\n其實你想知咩新手資料???大部分巴哈都有<br />\n<br />\n1. 每日我建議新手打龜仙人、Satan武道會、雲上活動，之後去攞獎品<br />\n<br />\n2. 如果係升Rank嘅，我估大家現在都係以力隊為主，請趁現在3倍經驗解主線Easy解到21-1(目覚めたさきに)，之後再解到呢關最高難度，力隊超4悟打體波易到爆，順便刷綠石(打蘭芝同畢拉夫)換下新手角<br />\n<br />\n3. 如果係打覺醒料，可以去覺醒活動關打<br />\n<br />\n4. 升到D卡咁上下，請先去解超本氣果關，每日打潛力解放材料<br />\n(開放條件:<br />\nA. Rank 50以上<br />\nB.「超本気の超決戦」ステージ2.激突！超サイヤ人孫悟空のZ-HARD Clear)<br />\n<br />\n5. 3倍經驗完左可以去刷每日強襲角，知、速角優先，刷的意思係講每隻刷10隻刷到10技，再刷多隻5技放倉，準備以後解超強襲.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n角色代號<br />\n感謝 格劍巴整合代號名單 <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rncalhpj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frncalhpj&h=e1d19c4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舊代號名單 感謝 photomore 巴打整合 <br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/19/031403_0f8104b2440ce5433f5504d1e13acd65.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F19%2F031403_0f8104b2440ce5433f5504d1e13acd65.jpg&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=00690237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/19/031403_0f8104b2440ce5433f5504d1e13acd65.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n限定點心紙<br />\n感謝 願你今夜別離去巴打整合<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3a7jv78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3a7jv78.jpg&h=6489d757&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n超激時間表<br />\n感謝 願你今夜別離去巴打整合<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gY57fC7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgY57fC7.jpg&h=0b84a2b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抽卡前請三思<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/25/032521_d685e28f3afbcdf8018b432c06024774.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F25%2F032521_d685e28f3afbcdf8018b432c06024774.jpg&h=ecb7e40d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf240cfad664145f8d0f37acd8f7d17a7278cca3","tid":245440,"uid":8300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T08:56:58.000Z","msg":"真係好難得...估唔到可以開晒2邊POST <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719445638c9ddc6ceb45778331f4d69976af1ddf","tid":245440,"uid":863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T08:58:44.000